TetrisLike3DSolver

Class LayeredContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Entities.Container
      • TetrisLike3DSolver.LayeredContainer

  • public class LayeredContainer
extends Container
    A derived container used to store the 3D pentominoes solutions. It's usable when the size of the pentominoes being stored allows for exact layering, using a divide and conquer approach. In our case, the pentominoes are made out of 0.5x0.5x0.5 boxes, so we can stack them in the 4.0 height of our container.
